title: Photoshop Training Video Part 3
description:
This is my 3rd home made Training Video for Photoshop and the best one yet!
I have included some more advanced tutorials while still making these descriptive and visual. I have steered away from signature tutorials and this video there is only one as I wanted to concentrate more on the tools available in Photoshop.
This video includes tutorials on 3D layers as well as Animation inside Photoshop.
All work files are included including the full 3ds files for 3D layers tutorial.
These videos are of good quality.
Please leave a comment and contact me via my site for any requests.
